gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: This feature dataset contains the following feature classes: NM_590_FALL_RESTRICT_WEB, NM_590_SOIL, NM_590_SWQMA_1000FT, NM_590_SWQMA_300FT, NM_590_WINT_RESTRICT_WEB, NM_CAFO_FALL_RESTRICT_WEB, NM_CAFO_SWQMA_300FT, NM_TRAIN_TERR. It is a feature dataset within the geodatabase, DATCP_NUTRIENT_MGMT.

gmd:purpose.gco:CharacterString: This feature dataset includes feature classes with data related to nutrient management in Wisconsin. The years of each individual feature class vary between 2012 - 2015.
